    "cnWords": "很久以前？这只打火机干干净净，没有一点灰尘和烟熏痕迹。在一间被烧成废墟的鞋坊里——它完好无损。这不像是遗落，更像是事后放进去的。",
    "enWords": "A long time ago? This lighter is spotless — not a speck of dust or smoke damage. In a shop burned to ruins, it's pristine. Doesn't look left behind. Looks planted.",
