    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "还有一位目击者——Rose Martinez。她说火灾当晚九点多，亲眼看到你从鞋坊出来，手里拿着一只打火机。",
    "enWords": "And there's an eyewitness — Rose Martinez. She says on the night of the fire, just after nine, she saw you coming out of the shoe shop, holding a lighter.",
